160
00:09:30,881 --> 00:09:33,281
Play along with me, okay?

161
00:09:33,281 --> 00:09:35,381
Conan!

162
00:09:35,381 --> 00:09:37,181
Yes, okay!

163
00:09:37,181 --> 00:09:41,181
I'll try asking the officers to do as you say, Pops!

164
00:09:41,181 --> 00:09:43,281
Okay, I'll leave it to you.

165
00:09:43,281 --> 00:09:46,281
Conan, no. He's not...

166
