00:10:41,368 --> 00:10:44,468
Just say it like I told you, and it'll be okay.

184
00:10:44,468 --> 00:10:46,268
Don't flinch.

185
00:10:48,168 --> 00:10:51,368
Make them believe that you're Sherlock Holmes.

