00:11:17,768 --> 00:11:20,068
Now, here's the third question!

197
00:11:20,068 --> 00:11:21,768
He hit it! It's a big one!

198
00:11:21,768 --> 00:11:23,368
It's zapping.

199
00:11:23,368 --> 00:11:25,368
What... What's going on?

200
00:11:26,468 --> 00:11:29,268
Somebody is actually in the room, right?

201
00:11:29,268 --> 00:11:32,468
-Wait! -Today is Christmas!

