00:24:08,968 --> 00:24:10,168
Hey!

438
00:24:10,168 --> 00:24:13,168
That's not for sale. Don't touch it!

439
00:24:13,168 --> 00:24:15,568
We were just looking around.

440
00:24:15,568 --> 00:24:16,868
Get out of here right this minute!

